node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Embroidery on tulle ♡ Мoscow on July 20, 2021 tagging @sardart.store. May be an image of cake.

node.text:
Guuuuys💛
Sale 15% off 🌼💛For all the gorgeous crystals until the end of this week 🌼

We were inspired by the shape and texture of natural crystals, but decided to add real flowers to them to make the final objects look really magic✨

Available in my shop on Etsy, link in bio 💛🌼
